{"tid":1020483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"環保撚有冇諗過收膠袋稅冇人屌 走飲管有人屌","createTime":"2019-02-13T15:39:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T00:33:07.000Z","uid":232237,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d48176a26e4b9e4eade4424c2dbd7b6f478c88","tid":1020483,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:39:31.000Z","msg":"根本收膠袋稅咁大影響都冇人日屌夜屌嫁<br />\n你地到底有冇反省過去點解自己咁神憎厭呀 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n環保4r 入面都係：<br />\n(一)減少使用（REDUCE） <br />\n(二)循環再造（RECYCLE）<br />\n(三)物盡其用（REUSE）<br />\n(四)替代使用（REPLACE)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇一個係冇撚得用嫁屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jcWuwtc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjcWuwtc.jpg&h=9845b1a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都算<br />\n屌你老母重要個光環道德高地企到都撚柒高<br />\n<br />\n你地不如環保d死撚曬佢<br />\n地球幾時冇左你個撚屌會轉唔到嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地咁搞落去香港環保運動一定愈來愈少人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n環保焦土<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　　　"},{"pid":"0cdf9715c2538156b2f9d59833f61a7c1264beda","tid":1020483,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T15:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46d32efaf9476439a1fbd08f717ebdf6dab06af2","tid":1020483,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T17:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35f8b302edd3b8b759d1677ab496ba0dc1e17aa9","tid":1020483,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply